title: The Jerk Theory 2009 (with greek subs)
description:
-THE JERK THEORY (2009) 
-The lead singer/guitarist of a high school rock band openly and unapologetically proclaims himself a newly converted jerk; however, the right girl comes along who could change him back to his former sweet self.

-Director: Scott S. Anderson
-Writers: Scott S. Anderson, Abraham Taylor
-Stars: Josh Henderson, Jenna Dewan-Tatum, Lauren Storm

MY PERSONAL FAVOURITE MOVIE ENJOY GUYS!
